msgstr ""

#: includes/class-simpletaxonomyrefreshed-admin-conversion.php:423
msgid "You identify the source taxonomy and the destination one and click on Copy Terms. This does not copy the terms, but prepares the data for the next phase - the Terms import tool."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-simpletaxonomyrefreshed-admin-conversion.php:424
msgid "If either taxonomy is non-hierarchical, it will extract all terms as a simple alphabetical list, otherwise it will prepare a hierarchical list."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-simpletaxonomyrefreshed-admin-conversion.php:425
msgid "The data extracted are then presented back to you in the form of a pre-filled input form."
msgstr ""

#: includes/class-simpletaxonomyrefreshed-admin-conversion.php:426
